## Document Purpose
Full technical diagnosis of the `kb.insightprofit.live` build crash for handoff to any coding tool (GenSpark, Hermes, Cursor, Codex, or manual developer). Contains reproduction steps, root cause analysis, every attempted fix, and recommended solutions ranked by risk.

