## 5. ALL ATTEMPTED FIXES (IN ORDER)

| # | Approach | Commit | Result | Why It Failed |
|---|----------|--------|--------|---------------|
| 1 | Pin Node to 22 LTS | `cabba59` | ❌ ERROR | Cache still invalidated; same prerender crash |
| 2 | Pin Node to 20 LTS | `4e59b9a` | ❌ ERROR | Same crash |
| 3 | Remove auth wall (AppShell/UserMenu) | `7c5033c` | ❌ ERROR | Auth wasn't the issue |
| 4 | Fix 72 content files (status: published → active) | `b07dbb5` | ❌ ERROR | Content schema wasn't the crash point |
| 5 | Fix 1,181 broken genspark EmbedBlock → valid Markdoc | `2db56d2` | ❌ ERROR | Invalid content causes rendering errors but not the prerender crash |
| 6 | Skip genspark pages from static prerender | `39f1236` | ❌ ERROR | `/_not-found` still prerendered |
| 7 | Skip ALL static prerender (`generateStaticParams = []`) | `de1fff2` | ❌ ERROR | `/_not-found` is always prerendered regardless |
| 8 | Filter genspark from nav tree (104 items in sidebar) | `b6e2ab0` | ❌ ERROR | Sidebar size wasn't the issue |
| 9 | Minimal layout (only Nextra Layout + 2 hardcoded items) | `a4127f5` | ❌ ERROR | Proved crash is IN Nextra Layout itself |
| 10 | Remove Nextra Layout entirely, use custom Sidebar | `ff3871b` | ❌ ERROR | New error: `Missing ConfigContext.Provider` on MDX pages |

**Key Insight from Attempt #9:** Even a completely minimal layout with ONLY the Nextra `<Layout>` component and 2 hardcoded pageMap entries crashes with the same `digest: 2150316170` on `/_not-found`. This eliminates ALL custom code, content volume, and data fetching as causes.

**Key Insight from Attempt #10:** Removing Nextra Layout reveals that all `.mdx` pages (e.g., `/ai-research/manus`) require `ConfigContext.Provider` from `nextra-theme-docs`. You can't just remove the Layout.

