## 12. SUCCESS CRITERIA

A successful fix must:
- [ ] `npm run build` completes without errors on Vercel (Node 22.x)
- [ ] `/_not-found` renders a proper 404 page (not a crash)
- [ ] All MDX pages render with Nextra's sidebar and styling
- [ ] KB Supabase pages (`/kb`, `/kb/[category]`, `/kb/item/[id]`) load
- [ ] Keystatic admin (`/keystatic`) is accessible
- [ ] No auth wall — all pages load without login
- [ ] Site is embeddable in Command Center iframes (CSP headers preserved)
- [ ] Pagefind search index builds successfully
- [ ] Build time under 5 minutes

